    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>   
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden noon<ptr target="nyp.00606_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1888-05-07">May 7 '88</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>I send you some papers to while away the time&#8212;Was out yesterday driving in the
                country&#8212;never did the spring impress me more&#8212;it was just the right
                temperature&#8212;the very sun &amp; wind and grass with sort o' human
                relations&#8212;(what a beautiful object is a young wheat field! what
                color!)&#8212;Had a good supper, oysters &amp; champagne, at my friends the
                    Harneds<ptr target="loc.03745_n1"/> in the evn'g&#8212;I only eat two meals a
                day&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
